      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，LA就是FinTech_PaymentGateway这个聚合节点对吧？那Logs到LA是单向流入，LA再并行输出到Workbooks和Alerts？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "LA",
